参考链接:https://github.com/lixianqiang/shadowsocks-libev#build-deb-package-from-source

方法1(脚本安装,已验证):
以下步骤均适用于服务端与客户端
1.下载源码包并进行安装
        git clone https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-libev.git
        cd shadowsocks-libev
        git submodule update --init --recursive
        mkdir -p ~/build-area/
        cp ./scripts/build_deb.sh ~/build-area/
        cd ~/build-area
        ./build_deb.sh
2.修改配置文件
        sudo vim /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json

以下步骤需根据情况对应操作
1.启动服务端(方法4选1)
        (1)sudo ss-server -c /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json start 
        (2)sudo /etc/init.d/shadowsocks-libev start   
        (3)sudo service shadowsocks-libev start       
        (4)sudo systemctl start shadowsocks-libev
2.启动客户端
        sudo ss-local -c /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json start

方法2(源码编译,未验证)
以下步骤均适用于服务端与客户端
1.pip安装shadowsocks-libev
        sudo apt-get install software-properties-common -y
        sudo add-apt-repository ppa:max-c-lv/shadowsocks-libev -y
        sudo apt-get update
        sudo apt install shadowsocks-libev
2.安装依赖库
        #安装加密库 libsodium-1.0.16
        export LIBSODIUM_VER=1.0.16
        wget https://download.libsodium.org/libsodium/releases/libsodium-$LIBSODIUM_VER.tar.gz
        tar xvf libsodium-$LIBSODIUM_VER.tar.gz
        pushd libsodium-$LIBSODIUM_VER
        ./configure --prefix=/usr && make
        sudo make install
        popd
        sudo ldconfig

        #安装 MbedTLS 
        export MBEDTLS_VER=2.6.0
        wget https://tls.mbed.org/download/mbedtls-$MBEDTLS_VER-gpl.tgz
        tar xvf mbedtls-$MBEDTLS_VER-gpl.tgz
        pushd mbedtls-$MBEDTLS_VER
        make SHARED=1 CFLAGS="-O2 -fPIC"
        sudo make DESTDIR=/usr install
        popd
        sudo ldconfig
3.修改配置文件
        sudo vim /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json

以下步骤需根据情况对应操作
1.启动服务端(方法4选1)
        (1)sudo ss-server -c /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json start 
        (2)sudo /etc/init.d/shadowsocks-libev start   
        (3)sudo service shadowsocks-libev start       
        (4)sudo systemctl start shadowsocks-libev
2.启动客户端
        sudo ss-local -c /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json start
        
        
               
参见问题
问题1: 客户端出现 类似[Errno 99] Cannot assign requested address
       检查是不是使用了类似sudo /etc/init.d/shadowsocks-libev start指令
       要的是客户端不是服务端，因此不是启动server，用另一个命令sudo ss-local
问题2: 客户端或服务端出现类似: ERROR: invalid cipher name: xchacha20-ietf-poly1305
                              ERROR: failed to initialize ciphers     
       证明加密库libsodium的版本不对(要求1.0.12以上)

